title: Woman Kneeling

adjectives: Represents calm, respectful, or meditative postures.
verbs: Depicts kneeling, resting, praying, or meditating.
nouns: A woman shown kneeling, often used to convey humility, prayer, meditation, or rest.

description: A woman shown kneeling on one or both knees. May represent prayer, meditation, humility, or resting on the floor. Often used in contexts of mindfulness, focus, or respect.
apple_vendor_description: On Apple devices, the woman kneeling emoji depicts a woman in a kneeling position, rendered with smooth gradients and realistic proportions. She conveys calmness, focus, and humility, symbolizing prayer, meditation, or respectful posture.
